    <item>
      <title>特朗普的最低关税10％使寻求交易的国家更加困难</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/nations-seeking-to-cut-trade-deals-with-trump-face-10-hurdle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的广泛关税宣布使外国领导人竞选与总统的交易，以降低对美国出口的关税。谈判窗口可能比他们想象的要小。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/nations-seeking-to-cut-trade-deals-with-trump-face-10-hurdle</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 17:00:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>敦促司法部不解散其重组的税款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/doj-is-urged-not-to-dissolve-its-tax-division-in-restructuring</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国前税务官员敦促美国司法部不要在机构范围内的重组中拆除其税收司，并警告说，这样的举动将妨碍执法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/doj-is-urged-not-to-dissolve-its-tax-division-in-restructuring</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 16:59:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大制造的汽车是免费的，保守派的保守派承诺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/conservatives-vow-to-waive-sales-tax-for-all-made-in-canada-cars</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保守党领导人皮埃尔·波利夫（Pierre Poilievre）承诺要删除对新加拿大制造的汽车的联邦销售税，并向特朗普政府的自动关税做出了回应，同时试图支持有危险的工人的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/conservatives-vow-to-waive-sales-tax-for-all-made-in-canada-cars</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 16:33:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>教育部门搬去改造学生债务计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/education-department-moves-to-revamp-student-debt-programs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国教育部正在启动一项规则制定程序，该程序可以使该机构大修多次联邦学生援助计划，这是唐纳德·特朗普总统一系列步骤中的最新步骤，以重塑向数百万美国借款人贷款的机构。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/education-department-moves-to-revamp-student-debt-programs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 16:13:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
